A vibrant, modern logo for the Turkish Mangala Mini App. The background is a deep navy blue gradient from top-left to bottom-right. In the center, a stylized white circle represents the game board, with six black dots arranged in two rows of three, each dot symbolizing a pit. Between the dots, a golden ring encircles the circle, symbolizing the store. Above the circle, a stylized Turkish flag ribbon in green and red curls upward, giving a sense of motion and national pride. The overall composition is clean, minimalistic, and instantly recognizable, suitable for a mobile app.
